              "settings": {
                "text": "<h2><strong>Join the Founders Club</strong></h2><p>Sign up before launch and you're in! The Founders Club is how we thank the people who join the brand early, and it never expires.</p><p>Members get:</p><ul><li>An invitation to the launch events at Darracott Farm (details below)</li><li>10% off every order. Not launch week, not your first order. Every order, for good.</li><li>Early access, and a number of other benefits reserved for the people who were here first</li></ul><p>One email is all it takes.</p>",
